dc:source  a    owl:AnnotationProperty .

gomodel:SYNGO_1953  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099056 replaced by GO:0042734" , "Rationale: PRRT2 is a transmembrane protein localized to presynaptic terminals in adult mouse forebrain.\nBiochemical fractionation from adult mouse cortices shows PRRT2 is enriched in a fraction that includes extrinsic and integral membrane proteins associated with the presynaptic area, is less abundant in the presynaptic active zone, and not detected in the postsynaptic density (Figure 1A). Further biochemical fractionation analyses from adult rat forebrain tissue shows PRRT2 associates with synaptic vesicles and and presynaptic membrane fractions, a similar distribution to that of SNAP-25 (Figure 1B). Immunostaining of exogenous PRRT2 (mCherry-PRRT2) in hippocampal neurons confirms synaptic localization of PRRT2 in intact cells (Figure 1C, PRRT2 co-localizes with synaptophysin and SNAP-25). Authors state there are currently no antibodies available that reliably detect endogenous PRRT2 in hippocampal cultures.\n\n5/12/2017 Pim\n- Based on the known transmembrane topology of the protein, the \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was chosen.. Experimental description: Subcellular fractionation (Figure 1A): adult mouse cortex (C57BL/6J mice of either sex from Charles River Laboratories) 3-6 months old\nSubcellular fractionation for SV purification. Subcellular fractions were prepared from rat forebrain (Sprague-Dawley rats either sex from Charles River Laboratories)\n\nImmunostaining: DIV 15 hippocampal neurons; Low-density and autaptic hippocampal neurons were prepared from C57BL6/J mice as previously described (Baldelli et al., 2007).\n\n5/12/2017 Pim\n- The species of the overexpressed/shRNA insensitive is not stated in the paper. Authors contacted for species information (fabio.benfenati@iit.it, dd. 5/12/2017). Authors answered:\n\n\"Mouse.\nI thought it was specified in the Supplementaries\nFabio Benfenati\"" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-9783-5183" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-5676-366X" ;
        dc:date           "2024-03-14" ;
        dc:title          "SYNGO_CC_1953" ;
        pav:providedBy    "https://syngo.vu.nl" ;
        biolink:in_taxon  "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/NCBITaxon_10090" .

